targets.rawSql: SELECT COUNT("Questions") FROM "Questions" WHERE "Timestamp" = CURRENT_DATE LIMIT 50
SELECT COUNT("Questions") FROM "Questions" WHERE "Timestamp" BETWEEN date_trunc('week', current_date) AND date_trunc('week', current_date) + interval '1 week'
SELECT COUNT("Questions") FROM "Questions" WHERE "Timestamp" BETWEEN date_trunc('month', current_date) AND date_trunc('month', current_date) + interval '1 month'
SELECT COUNT("Questions"), "Timestamp" FROM "Questions" GROUP BY "Timestamp" LIMIT 50
SELECT "Keywords", "Frequency" FROM "Keywords" ORDER BY "Frequency" DESC LIMIT 10
